newsitem.title: USA: IMM currency futures end dull trade barely mixed.
newsitem.headline: IMM currency futures end dull trade barely mixed.

text.p: IMM currency futures ended a session of low-volume pit trading barely mixed.
Traders said futures ferreted out few fresh features to focus on as the day progressed, with traders fixated on this week's early market finishes for the Christmas holiday.
Chicago Mercantile Exchange futures close at 1200 CST/1800 GMT Tuesday and will remain shut on December 25.
Volume was estimated on the price boards at only 3,800, 4,700 and 4,300 in March marks, yen and Swiss, respectively.
"There is absolutely no paper interest whatsoever," complained a floor broker. "It's all dealer-to-dealer."
